                                                <p><strong>Step 2:</strong></p>
                                                <p><strong>Adjust</strong> the pillow so each side firmly supports your
                                                    belly and lower back</p>
                                                <p><strong>Step 3: </strong></p>
                                                <p><strong>Enhance</strong> comfort by placing the mini-knee pillow
                                                    (sold separately) between your legs for full-body alignment</p>
